==Korean==
===Noun===
'''구멍''' {gumeong}

#[[hole]]
#:바지에 '''구멍'''이 났다. (''baji-e gumeong-i nattda'') &mdash; [I’ve] got a hole in my trousers. (literally, "a hole appeared in my trousers.")
#:벽에 '''구멍'''을 뚫다. (''byeog-e '''gumeong'''eul ddulta'') &mdash; Drill a '''hole''' in a wall.

====Related terms====
*[[오존 구멍]] (''ojon gumeong'') &mdash; ozone hole
*[[거믄구멍]] (''geomeun gumeong'') &mdash; [[black hole]]

